grinder and just buff all the crap off. It seems like 3M's also got
some alternatives to wire brush wheels. I didn't want to spend a whole
lot of time on this, but at the same time I didn't want to put them back
in the engine all cruddy when I've cleaned the rest of the engine ;)
 
